Package: SphereOptimize
Type: Package
Title: Optimization On A Unit Sphere
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yijun Xie
Maintainer: Yijun Xie <yijun.xie@uwaterloo.ca>
Description: This package provides a simple tool for numerical optimization on the unit sphere. This is achieved by combining the spherical coordinating system with L-BFGS-B optimization.
